## 2. Implementation Details

### 2.1 Data Collection
```python
# Sample data collection code
for action in ['hello', 'thanks', 'iloveyou']:
    for sequence in range(30):
        for frame_num in range(30):
            # Capture frame and save keypoints
            keypoints = extract_keypoints(results)
            np.save(os.path.join('MP_Data', action, str(sequence), str(frame_num)), keypoints)
```

### 2.2 Model Architecture
```python
model = Sequential([
    LSTM(64, return_sequences=True, input_shape=(30,1662)),
    LSTM(128, return_sequences=True),
    LSTM(64),
    Dense(64, activation='relu'),
    Dense(32, activation='relu'), 
    Dense(3, activation='softmax')
])
```

